    <section data-background="#e6f0fa">
        <div class="question-box">
            <p style="font-size:1.2em; margin:0;"><strong>Challenge: How do you swap two variables (A and
                    B)?</strong></p>
            <p class="small-text">Imagine A is a cup of Water, B is a cup of Tea. You can't mix them.</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
        <div class="question-box">
            <p><strong>Step 1:</strong> You need a third cup (Temp).</p>
            <p><code>temp = a</code> (Pour A into Temp)</p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
        <div class="question-box">
            <p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Pour B into A.</p>
            <p><code>a = b</code></p>
        </div>
    </section>
    <section>
        <div class="question-box">
            <p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Pour Temp (original A) into B.</p>
            <p><code>b = temp</code></p>
